They call them gay, call them weak and be racist towards them. Please stop replying to the post shipping idols because imagine someone shipped you with a person you believe is you friend. Stop replying to such video's and stop making disgusting edits for fun, cuz you know what? Its not fun! You know what happened to Stray Kids when they attended the Met Gala, and what usually happens to BTS on the internet and Blackpink. I daily encounter 4-5 approx. shorts/reels hating on BTS. Like comparing them with their favourite football idols and lot more, and the comments are like, proud to be a hater, kpop hater etc. So now please, listen carefully, to stop this we first have to stop the fight among ourselves. Like btw diff kpop stans. Like we need to stop hating different groups or stop fighting like, "No bts is the best!" No, its Blackpink!" Stop it. We need to unite. Everyone we need to stop hating the groups that are not our favourite's. EVERYONE HAS THEIR FAVORITE GROUP. Next step is very important. We need to stop reacting or commenting on Kpop hate vids. Or reply any hateful comment or write any comment defending your favs. For eg. You saw an edit a guy is comparing bts with ronaldo/messi etc. and he disrespected bts in that, don't react don't comment just stop. You don't to write any comment in that post. Nor you have to reply to those shit comments, just ignore. Report that video/short/reel that's it! Simple. Please baby stans, please stop fighting everywhere. AND WRITING COMMENTS LIKE: Blackpink the best, JENNIE, KIM TAEHYUNG everywhere. Please, it's just so cringe and shows how immature you are. Stop crying everywhere" Ohh why u hate BTS" Stop creating cringe edits and FANFICTIONS. Stop giving time to these teenage boy's shitty opinions who think they are chads and sigma by hating. And at last, all kpop fans, let's make a promise we won't hate each other. Respect each other and our opinions. Stop arguing and giving time to haters. Because the more you react. THE MORE THEY CREATE SUCH CONTENT. We also need to stop being creepy towards our idols. are our idols, not our husband/wife. Lets try to make the kpop community a better place. Please. ARMYS, Let's make our four talented vocalists the first four for the best Kpop vocalist vote! Also, continue to vote for Taetae for the most handsome man, BTS leading for the EXO vs BTS, BTS as the best Male Kpop group, BTS for Blackpink vs BTS*, best Kpop song -> FRI(END)S, best rappers with our rap kings being the top three, Suga for Liam Payne vs Suga, RM as the best leader(Top famous and Shining Awards), RM for Harry Styles vs RM, Jungkook for Liam Payne Vs Jungkook, V for V vs Niall Horan, Jin for Jin vs Zayn Malik, Jimin for Jimin vs Louis Tomlinson, Jhope for Jhope vs Louis Tomlinson, BTS for BTS vs One Direction, V for V vs Justin Bieber and any other voting involving BTS and other artists! Let's do our best! *EXTREMELY IMPORTANT, they're catching up! If possible, stream "Never Let Go", "LOST!", "Nuts", "Come Back To Me", "NEURON", "MORE", "Haegeum", "Daechwita", "Seven", "Like Crazy", "Love Me Again", "The Astronaut", "Dynamite", "Butter" (Proof Album), "My Universe", "FAKE LOVE", "Left and Right" as much as possible. Good job to those who kept streaming! The monthly listeners are increasing day by day. Also, please don't show hate to the idols like Jennie or Jisso, or Red Velvet's member Yeri , Nancy, Soyeon, Eunwoo, Exo's Kai, TWICE Tzuyu, IZ*ONE Sakura, IU, Mamamoo Hwasa and EXO's Chen. They are all amazing singers and dancers just like any other k-pop idol. Don't hate other grps if you like one the most. They all play an equal role. And please stop comparing idols, each one os them is a different and unique rose in the garden of K-pop. Pin Please :)
